  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Stay self-catered and make the most of the kitchen and open plan living space in your apartment. The nearest supermarket is located just across the road from the apartment building.</p>
<p>There's also the option to upgrade to half board and enjoy breakfast and dinner delivered directly to your apartment in Levi Black. A Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration with games and music. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
