  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Levi Black Apartments are located just outside Levi. They are modern, comfortable choice for a Lapland holiday with excellent facilities, including a fully equipped kitchen, private sauna and public outdoor whirlpools. Available on a self catering or half board basis.</p>]]></listingDescription>
