  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Levi Black Apartments </strong>sleep 6-8 people. Each apartment has two floors, four twin bedrooms (one of the rooms is internal, no windows), an open plan living area with kitchen-diner and lounge area, two toilets (one on each floor), a shower room and a private sauna. The first floor includes the open plan living space, one twin bedroom (internal), a sauna and shower room and a separate toilet. Upstairs there are 3 twin bedrooms and a toilet with a shower. </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchen equipped with crockery, oven and stove, microwave, kettle, coffee making facilities, fridge/freezer and a dishwasher</li>
<li>Linen (beds made) and towels</li>
<li>Private sauna </li>
<li>Flat screen TV</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>A typical apartment floorplan:</strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 719px; height: 315px;" src="/media/13100441/levi-black_apartments-floor-plan.jpg?width=719&amp;height=315&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5628acbb1bf245ed9b4d79a2c3c63618" /></p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
